{"title":"An economist as interim leader of Bangladesh","link":"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/902450216/0/marginalrevolution~An-economist-as-interim-leader-of-Bangladesh.html","date":1722977579000,"content":"<blockquote>\r\n<p>The president of Bangladesh on Tuesday appointed <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.nytimes.com/2024/08/06/world/asia/bangladesh-protests-muhammad-yunus.html\">Muhammad Yunus</a>, a pioneer in microfinance and a Nobel laureate, to oversee an interim government, accommodating demands by protesters and offering a reprieve for a country scarred by violence.</p>\r\n<p>The plans for a new government were announced a day after Bangladesh’s authoritarian leader, Sheikh Hasina, resigned and fled the country amid a popular uprising.</p>\r\n</blockquote>\r\n<p>Here is <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://www.nytimes.com/2024/08/06/world/asia/bangladesh-government.html\" target=\"_blank\">more from the NYT</a>.</p>\r\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com/marginalrevolution/2024/08/an-economist-as-interim-leader-of-bangladesh.html\">An economist as interim leader of Bangladesh</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://marginalrevolution.com\">Marginal REVOLUTION</a>.</p>\r\n<img height=\"1\" width=\"1\" src=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/i/902450216/0/marginalrevolution\" />\r\n<div><a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/28/902450216/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/fblike20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/29/902450216/marginalrevolution,\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/pinterest20.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.feedblitz.com/_/24/902450216/marginalrevolution\"><img height=\"20\" src=\"https://assets.feedblitz.com/i/x.png\" /></a> <a href=\"https://feeds.f